Date: Mon, 10 Mar 2025 16:53:33 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] staging: vchiq_arm: Don't use %pK through printk
Precedence: bulk
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
List-Id: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
